RewriteRule ^context$ https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Language-Research-Technology/language-data-commons-vocabs/master/ontology-context.json [R=302,L,QSA]
RewriteRule ^pilars$ https://pilars-protocols.github.io/pilars/ [R=302,L,QSA]
RewriteRule ^collections-profile$ https://github.com/Language-Research-Technology/generic-collection-profile/blob/main/profile/profile.md [R=302,L,QSA]